            "reference": {
                "value": "5993189"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "preparation",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p>Decide what you are going to write about; a whodunnit or a romantic chicklit story.</p>\n<p>You whodunnit/thriller could start with a strange disappearance or unexplained murder.</p>\n<p>Your chicklit could start with a surprise visit or mysterious person.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>First, write a short outline. Include the following information for your story:</p>\n<p>1. Who is the main character/suspect? And who else are involved?</p>\n<p>2. What happened?</p>\n<p>3. Where and when did it take place?</p>\n<p>4. Which possible explanations are there for the whodunnit/which different scenarios are possible for the romantic story?</p>\n"
                },
                {
                    "type": "image",
                    "src": "https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/1/18ebe3fbc8a266f5dd8cde6e5ccbfe9152e97b1e.jpg",
                    "altText": "",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "scale": 0.3,
                    "link": ""
                }
            ],
            "sections": []
        },
        {
            "reference": {
                "value": "5993277"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Writing your entry",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p>Write your story. Make sure:</p>\n<p>1. you give a catchy title.</p>\n<p>2. Write an interesting story.</p>\n<p>3. Write at least 600 words.</p>\n<p>4. Make your story interesting to read.</p>\n<p>5. Watch your grammar and use the appropriate vocabulary.</p>\n"
                },
                {
                    "type": "image",
                    "src": "https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/9/923671ec290bbcde76c6d47f09cb8ada783dace5.jpg",
                    "altText": "",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "scale": 0.3,
                    "link": ""
                }
            ],
            "sections": []
        },
        {
            "reference": {
                "value": "5993312"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Evaluation",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<div>Your teacher gives you a grade based on 4 things (which all are graded 0-5 marks):</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div><strong>Content</strong> - Did you write what you were asked to write?</div>\n<div><strong>Communicative achievement</strong> - Was your writing too formal, too informal, or just right?</div>\n<div><strong>Organisation</strong> - Did you link paragraphs and sentences? Is there a logical flow from start to finish?</div>\n<div><strong>Language</strong> - Did you show off your sparkling vocabulary or did you use basic words? Did you make lots of grammar and spelling mistakes?</div>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": []
        }
